asset.title: 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013, 2014 Ford Mustang Shelby GT500 V8 Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to your 2010-2014 Ford Mustang Shelby GT500 V8 with this K&N air intake system. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-2579

This intake system created an estimated gain of 30 horsepower and 31 lb. ft. of torque at 5,200 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 63-2579 fits the following: 
2014 FORD MUSTANG SHELBY GT500 5.8L V8 
2013 FORD MUSTANG SHELBY GT500 5.8L V8 
2012 FORD MUSTANG SHELBY GT500 5.4L V8 
2011 FORD MUSTANG SHELBY GT500 5.4L V8 
2010 FORD MUSTANG SHELBY GT500 5.4L V8

http://www.KNfilters.com
